{"id": "1256543619628662784", "channel_id": "1252547613320941642", "type": 0, "author_id": "1045141709580927067", "author_name": "luoqixikiss", "author_bot": false, "content": "你要知道米粒的狂气充能是给队友的，而不是给你的，后面米粒要回初始版本，灵知给狂气只有一次了，这200超限还得是等到深海队来米粒之外一个能充狂气的角色才好用。", "timestamp": "2024-06-29T09:35:44.371000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1252547613320941642", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "「彌利亞姆」體驗交流分享活動", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1202451003690188860"]}
{"id": "1256544155417706572", "channel_id": "1252547613320941642", "type": 0, "author_id": "1045141709580927067", "author_name": "luoqixikiss", "author_bot": false, "content": "再一提，米粒强度还是很猛的吧，特别是配上专属银匙，深海队只要有算力就可以为所欲为，活动2回合把米粒三个阶段全开了，6回合近1000触伤满爆，满血虐死boos了", "timestamp": "2024-06-29T09:37:52.113000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1256544155367112795", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-06-29-17-29-53-67_1c2ea364798f98bd84a81a8c53b45cfb.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 232197, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1252547613320941642/1256544155367112795/Screenshot_2024-06-29-17-29-53-67_1c2ea364798f98bd84a81a8c53b45cfb.jpg?ex=69cb95f0&is=69ca4470&hm=ad9eedf5c0f9461975275ae1e1765fdf950b65244e862d005c93815fba2fc393&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1252547613320941642", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "「彌利亞姆」體驗交流分享活動", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1202451003690188860"]}
{"id": "1256544226209173596", "channel_id": "1252547613320941642", "type": 0, "author_id": "1045141709580927067", "author_name": "luoqixikiss", "author_bot": false, "content": "但是前提是有算力", "timestamp": "2024-06-29T09:38:08.991000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1252547613320941642", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "「彌利亞姆」體驗交流分享活動", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1202451003690188860"]}
{"id": "1256554774598385704", "channel_id": "1252547613320941642", "type": 0, "author_id": "1130173030505648160", "author_name": "gehuoku_86898", "author_bot": false, "content": "？你从3启抽到能超限还要抽4只吧，你不是随便氪8+16的富哥那还是算了，为了一个米粒的超限氪那么多，打融灾要19个角色，打深浅0+1米粒就能3w分了。\n还是那句话，不是特别有钱的人，不要硬氪到深化4", "timestamp": "2024-06-29T10:20:03.923000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1252547613320941642", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "「彌利亞姆」體驗交流分享活動", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1202451003690188860"]}
{"id": "1256555597583749122", "channel_id": "1252547613320941642", "type": 0, "author_id": "1130173030505648160", "author_name": "gehuoku_86898", "author_bot": false, "content": "哪有劝人这样氪金的，如果你氪了之后给米粒抽到深化4了，感觉后悔了，又不能退款，谁能给你负责？难道继续抽16个命轮？", "timestamp": "2024-06-29T10:23:20.138000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1252547613320941642", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "「彌利亞姆」體驗交流分享活動", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1202451003690188860"]}
